intro.title: Family-Owned, Island-Inspired
intro.p1: A & S Distributors is a family owned business committed to serving our family of customers who depend on us for the highest quality foods from Fiji, New Zealand & Australia. We are the Northern California Distributor for The New Zealand Lamb Company and have our own USDA facility for cutting all goat and lamb varieties. We carry a variety of fresh, frozen and dry Pacific Island specialty foods at competitive prices.
intro.p2: At A & S Distributors we strive for excellence by building lasting relationships with our customers through our commitment to integrity and respect. We are dedicated to consistently helping stores provide quality products their customers will use to make delicious meals for their families.
intro.p3: We strive to provide a level of service that not only delivers the products our customers need but also includes a commitment to ensure accuracy of your orders. Going the "extra mile" is what sets A & S Distributors apart from our competitors. We look forward to working with you.
